Basic Installation
==================

Compiling on Windows platform
-----------------------------

Using Visual C++ 2003:

  1. Open [yake]/scripts/yake/yake.sln and do a "Build All"
  2. Do the same for [yake]/scripts/yapp/yapp.sln
  
  This will build all the libraries and samples.

Compiling Linux platform
------------------------

Please see the file [yake]/scripts/linux/INSTALL for details.

